# Photo Style

When generating or selecting photos for this project, follow the We-Commerce photo style.

Read `wecommerce-photo-style-guide.md` for the full analysis and ready-to-use Gemini prompts.

## Quick Reference

> Warm Portra 400 film look — muted amber tones, soft natural light, shallow depth of field, candid diverse people using phones in casual lifestyle settings, with lifted milky shadows and subtle grain.

### Always
- Warm muted desaturated colors, amber-golden tones
- Soft natural light (window light, golden hour), no flash
- Shallow depth of field, creamy bokeh
- Lifted milky shadows, subtle film grain
- Candid authentic moments, not posed
- Earth-toned wardrobe: cream, beige, olive, rust, sage
- Casual settings: cafes, home offices, city streets, couches

### Never
- Saturated/neon/vibrant colors
- Studio lighting, flash, ring lights
- High contrast, HDR, smooth digital look
- Corporate settings, boardrooms, gyms
- Posed/editorial/formal aesthetic
- Bright wardrobe, suits, formal wear
